import React from "react";
import { Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";


import InputModel from "./components/InputModel.jsx"
import Pin from "./components/Pin.jsx"
import PPICW1 from "./components/PPIC&QCW1/PPIC.jsx"
import QCW1 from "./components/PPIC&QCW1/QC.jsx"

import PPICW2 from "./components/PPIC&QCW2/PPIC.jsx"
import QCW2 from "./components/PPIC&QCW2/QC.jsx"

import PPICW3 from "./components/PPIC&QCW3/PPIC.jsx"
import QCW3 from "./components/PPIC&QCW3/QC.jsx"

import PPICW4 from "./components/PPIC&QCW4/PPIC.jsx"
import QCW4 from "./components/PPIC&QCW4/QC.jsx"




import PPICU1 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW1/PPIC.jsx"
import QCU1 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW1/QC.jsx"

import PPICU2 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW2/PPIC.jsx"
import QCU2 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW2/QC.jsx"

import PPICU3 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW3/PPIC.jsx"
import QCU3 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW3/QC.jsx"

import PPICU4 from "./components/User/PPIC&QCW4/PPIC.jsx"
import QCU4 from "./components/PPIC&QCW4/QC.jsx"



function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Routes>
      <Route path="/" element={<Pin/>}/>
        <Route path="PPICW1" element={<PPICW1/>}/>
        <Route path="QCW1" element={<QCW1/>}/>
        <Route path="PPICW2" element={<PPICW2/>}/>
        <Route path="QCW2" element={<QCW2/>}/>
        <Route path="PPICW3" element={<PPICW3/>}/>
        <Route path="QCW3" element={<QCW3/>}/>
        <Route path="PPICW4" element={<PPICW4/>}/>
        <Route path="QCW4" element={<QCW4/>}/>
        <Route path="Pin" element={<Pin/>}/>
        <Route path="InputModel" element={<InputModel/>}/>
      </Routes>
    </>
  );
}

export default App;
